original: Högberg, Gunnar Ossian, tf. kyrkoherde, Hunnestad, f. 3/2/98 i Sol-berga, Gbgs o. Boh. 1., av kyrkoh. Lars Emanuel H. o. Anna Gustava Svens’Son. G. 29 m. Gertrud Lind-hardt. Barn: Ingrid f. 30, Lars-Olof 33, CeciHa 34, Alvar 38. — Stud:ex. i Halmstad 16, teol. kand. i Lund samt prästex. o. prästv. i Gbg 20. V. pastor i Foss 20, i Naverstad 20-21, i Mor-landa 21-22, ord. kommin. i Skee sed. 22, vakanskyrkoh. i Hunnestad ’sed. 46.
translated: Högberg, Gunnar Ossian, temporary vicar, Hunnestad, born February 3rd, 1898 in Solberga, Gothenburg and Bohus county, son of the vicar Lars Emanuel Högberg and Anna Gustava Svens'Son. Married Gertrud Lindhardt in 1929. Children: Ingrid born in 1930, Lars-Olof born in 1933, Cecilia born in 1934, Alvar born in 1938. Studied in Halmstad, graduating in 1916, then studied theology in Lund and completed his priestly exams in Gothenburg in 1920. Worked as an assistant pastor in Foss in 1920, in Naverstad in 1920-21, in Morlanda in 1921-22, and as an ordained curate in Skee starting from 1922. Became the interim vicar in Hunnestad in 1946.
